      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IDEAL BANDIT (9) brings strong form from Victoria having made it two wins on the trot when he got the cash by 5 metres last week at Melton. Can travel in a nice spot from this draw and wait on the sprint lane if necessary. Proven here and strikes at 50 per cent at the distance so can chalk-up the hat-trick. VIN NUMBER (10) has been racing well in stronger company, missing by only 2m two back and placing last week, both at this circuit and distance. Draws on the back line but is suited in this grade. NORMS LADY (1) is coming back in class and gets the ace draw again so is worth another chance. OCTAGONISE (6) hasn't been far away at his last couple and finds a more suitable assignment.",
